Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The capture of General Noriega, 1990
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yg310
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 5 Jan 1990
With General Noriega of Panama captured by US forces, Alistair Cooke chronicles the American dealings with Noriega and the relationship between the two countries.